@WIDTH 80
@NODE MAIN "Protector"

                                 ProtectorV1.92
                               BBS-Safety-Utility

 As you can see in the history, there was a long delay between version 1.7 and
    version 1.8. Before v1.8 I released a new version every three months and
 version 1.8 was nearly finished after this time, too. But as really nobody has
 send me anything (no mails, no registration, NOTHING) since releasing version
 1.6, I lost my interest in this project and I haven't released _anything_ for
 over one year. But it made me sick to have some nice tools and only one user,
     myself. So I startet to release my work again and I also finished the
 protector. It now has all the features I need and is running smoothly, so this
                           will be the final release.

 Because V1.8 does not work correct with gfxcards, I made another release which
                           should solve the problem.

          With release 2.0 95% of all known bugs should be removed :-)

