===============================================================================
@NODE SHUTDOWN
                                    SHUTDOWN

     The @{"shutdownsystem" LINK COPYRIGHT} from @{"Olaf Barthel" LINK THANX} delay`s a reset as long as it
   is needed to stop all fileaccess. To use the full functions of this system
  you have to install it completely. The shutdown.library is only delivered in
 this packet to garant the useability of the Protector. To use all the features
          of shutdown, you have to get the full packet and install it.

@ENDNODE
